data.title: Henley Shull Resume Teaching
data.meta_description: henley shull resume teaching - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Henley P Shull received a Bachelor's degree in Psychology and a Master's degree in Elementary Education from the University of Virginia. She has experience teaching grades K-6 as a student teacher, substitute teacher in the U.S., Australia, and as a full time teacher. Her experience includes teaching at a charter school in California as well as substitute teaching positions in Virginia and Australia. She also has experience as a camp counselor and lifeguard.
